table.name: cdp_sys_parameter
table.Comment: 用于存放各种分类分组的个性化参数

table.name: cdp_sys_permission
table.Comment: 包含菜单、按钮两种权限

table.name: cdp_sys_user_permission
table.Comment: 用于增减用户的单项权限，通常实在角色的基础上增减单项权限

column.name: status
column.Comment: 0：正常状态 1：修改状态 2：删除状态

column.name: createFrom
column.Comment: 参数来源： 1：手动创建 2：系统创建

column.name: type
column.Comment: '0：按钮，对于url是http(s)后台请求 1：组件菜单，对应ur是前端组件l 2：链接菜单，对应url是http(s)链接地址',

column.name: app_name
column.Comment: 应用名称,等同于配置文件中的spring.application.name

column.name: trace_id_high
column.Comment: If non zero, this means the trace uses 128 bit traceIds instead of 64 bit

column.name: a_value
column.Comment: BinaryAnnotation.value(), which must be smaller than 64KB

column.name: a_timestamp
column.Comment: Used to implement TTL; Annotation.timestamp or zipkin_spans.timestamp

column.name: endpoint_ipv6
column.Comment: Null when Binary/Annotation.endpoint is null, or no IPv6 address

column.name: trace_id_high
column.Comment: If non zero, this means the trace uses 128 bit traceIds instead of 64 bit

column.name: start_ts
column.Comment: Span.timestamp(): epoch micros used for endTs query and to implement TTL

column.name: duration
column.Comment: Span.duration(): micros used for minDuration and maxDuration query
